title: Arthur C. Clarke's Mysterious World Disc 1/2
description:
Arthur C. Clarke's Mysterious World first DVD - double sided 7.46GB
Includes episodes 1 to 6:
- The Journey begins...
- Monsters of the Deep
- Ancient Wisdom
- The Missing Apeman
- Giants for the Gods
- The Monsters of the Lakes
Total: 325 mins approx.

DVD PAL - Region 2
Picture: 1.33:1 Colour
Subtitles: None.
Sound: Mono
Language: English (and some strange northern accents...)

A 1980 ITV production, DVD published by Netowrk (www.networkdvd.co.uk).

Burn all files on a double-layed DVD under a directory named VIDEO_TS, or you can transform the VOB files into AVI's.
